quran[29]{c,v,t}:
  17,99,Mbega ntibabonye yuko Imana yaremye Amajuru n’Isi ikaba ariyo ifise ubushobozi bw’ukurema abameze nkabo? Kandi yaraba shiriyeho umwanya udafise amakenga mugabo abahemukiye imitima yabo y’ukuri barahakanye ibintu vyose atari ukubandanya n’ubuhakanyi bwabo gusa
  17,100,"Vuga uti:- mbega iyo muganza ububiko hamwe n’imigisha y’Umuremyi wanyu, ntankeka mwari kuzitira mugutinya kuyakoresha, n’umuntu n’ingumyi cane"
  17,101,"Mu vy’ukuri twarahaye intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) ivyemezo bishika icenda biri kumugaragaro, ariko ni mubabaze bene Israeri mugihe yabashikira hamwe na Fir’auni ababwi ati:- mu vy’ukuri jewe ndakubona yuko wewe Mussa (iii) warozwe"
  17,102,"Intumwa y’Imana Mussa (iii) yishura Fir’auni iti :- ntankeka wewe uramaze kumenya yuko atawamanuye ibi ivyemezo nk’ibi atari Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi, kuba arivyo vyemezo mu vy’ukuri jewe ndakubona yuko wewe Fir’auni umaze kuba uri mubantu batakaye"
  17,103,"Rero Fir’auni yashatse kubirukana mugihugu cabo, kuri ivyo twaciye tumwibiza hamwe nabo bari kumwe nabo bose"
  17,104,"Hanyuma munyuma yaho twabwiye bene Israeri duti:- nimwicare muri iki gisagara nihashika isango ry’umusi w’umuhero w’Isi tuzoba zana mwese muri hamwe"
  17,105,"Kubera ukuzana ukuri kwama ngaha kw’Isi niho twamanuye iyi yamanutse, kandi ntitwakuzanye ngo ube umutanzi w’amakuru meza n’uwutuza"
  17,106,"N’iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu twayigabuye mwo ibice bitandukanye kugira ngo ubasomere abantu kugituro n’ikindi, kandi twayimanuye buhoro buhoro kugira ngo yorohe gufata mumutwe"
  17,107,"Vuga uti:- ni mwemere iyi Qur’ani canke ntimuyemere, mu vy’ukuri bamwe bahawe ubumenyi imbere yukumanuka kw’iyi Qur’ani ntagatifu, mugihe bayisomewe baca barwa hasi bubamye n’ugushira imitwe yabo hasi"
  17,108,"Bavuga bati:- Umuremyi wacu n’umutagatifu, mu vy’ukuri indagano itangwa n’Umuremyi wacu irakwiye"
  17,109,"Bama barwa hasi bubamye, bararira n’ukubongereza ubugamburutsi ntangere"
  17,110,"Vuga uti:- nimusabe kw’izina ry’Imana canke musabe kw’izina rya nyene imigisha canke kw’izina iryariryo ryose muyi hamagarira ko, kuko ifise amazina meza meza, kandi ntusome iyi Qur’ani kw’ijwi rininiya, canke ntuyisome kw’ijwi rigufiya, nawe uri muma sengesho yawe mu vy’ukuri ahubwo nufate inzira iri hagati y’izo"
  17,111,"Kandi uvuge uti:- ihayagizwa ryiza ryose niryo rikwiye Imana, kuko itigiriye ikibondo, kandi idafise umufasha mubwami bwayo, kandi ntamugenzi ifise kubera ukuti shobora kwayo bw’ugukenera icarico cose, kandi uhayagize kwihayagizwa rimwe rininiya"
  18,1,"Ndakengurukiye Imana yamanuriye umushumvyi wayo iki gitabu gitagatifu, kandi ntiyakigize ngo kibemwo amahinyu"
  18,2,"Giteguwe neza kugira ngo gituze abantu kubijanye n’ibihano bivuye ku Mana, kandi kibahe inkuru nziza bamwe bemera ari nabo bagira ibikorwa vyiza yuko bazoronka impembo nziza"
  18,3,Bazobamwo mubuzima bwabo bwose
  18,4,"Hanyuma ico gitabu kibatuze bamwe bavuga bati:- Imana yarigiriye ikibondo"
  18,5,"Ntabumenyi bafise buri hejuru yiri jambo canke abavyeyi babo, kandi n’ijambo rihambaye rivuye muminwa yabo, kandi ntibashobora kuvuga atari ububeshi gusa"
  18,6,"Kumbure wota umutima wawe mw’ihumbi kubera agahinda, n’ingene nabo batemera ibiganiro vyacu ubashikiriza"
  18,7,"Mu vy’ukuri twebwe twagize ibiri hejuru y’Isi ngo bibe arivyo bisharizo vyaryo, kugira ngo turabe uwariwe muribo mubagira ibikorwa vyiza cane"
  18,8,"Mu vy’ukuri ni twebwe tugira gutyo kubiri hejuru yiy’Isi, kuba ari Isi y’ubugararwe"
  18,9,Mbega wiyumvira yuko abantu bo mw’Isenga hamwe n’abafise amakuru yanditswe mubitabu bari mubantu b’ibitangaza vyacu
  18,10,"Iyo misore mugihe yirukira mw’isenga baciye bavuga bati:- Muremyi wacu, n’uduhe imigisha ivuye kuri wewe, kandi utugirire uburokoke kubintu vyacu vyose"
  18,11,Duca tuziba amatwi yabo bari mw’isenga kukiringo c’imyaka mwinshi cane
  18,12,Hanyuma turabazura kugira ngo tumenyeshe igiki kiri muri iyo mirwi uko ari ibiri yaharuye neza na neza ikiringo babayeyo muri iryo senga
  18,13,"Twebwe tukumenyesha inkuru zabo z’ukuri, kuko mu vy’ukuri iyo miyabaga bari mubemeye Umuremyi wabo bimwe bivuye k’umutima, natwe turabongereza uburokoke"
  18,14,"Hanyuma tubaha inguvu mumitima yabo mugihe bahagarara bavuga bati:- Umuremyi wacu n’Umuremyi w’Amajuru n’Isi, na twebwe ntituzo kwigera dusenga narimwe iyindi Mana itari Imana yonyene y’ukuri, ntankeka twebwe tuzoba twavuze ikinyoma kigaritse"
  18,15,"Aba bantu bacu bagize izindi Mana atari Imana y’ukuri, none ni kuki batazana hejuru yabo ivyemezo biri k’umugaragaro, none ni nde muhemu mukuru gusumba uwubeshera Imana y’ukuri"
  18,16,"Mugihe mwari mwavavanuye nabo hamwe n’ivyo basenga aho gusenga Imana y’ukuri, rero nimwirukire mw’isenga niho Umuremyi wanyu azobugururira imigisha yayo, nuku borohereza mubintu vyanyu vyose"